<br>
ATTACK<br>
-Speed casting time by 10% across the board. 6.3 seconds is unacceptable for a blast, that's longer than gate.<br>
-Lower mana cost for all blasts by 10% or more, resulting in even more efficient spells. Less mana cost = no need for faster mana regeneration for Wizards.<br>
<br>
(Focus items from mages and various drops address this to varied degrees of success)<br>
<br>
TELEPORTATION<br>
-Add a Velious translocate to Iceclad.<br>
<br>
(they went nuts and added tons of transloacates in)<br>
<br>
-Move WK porter to other side of zone.<br>
<br>
(they moved the evac point to the Qeynos Hills Zone and added a lower level evac that allows everyone who can get to WK porter to get there)<br>
<br>
SEEKING KNOWLEDGE<br>
-fix Eye of Zomm to have a 'sneak' like effect so that it can move past creatures if it does not come close (in other words, make its aggro radius smaller, so you can aggro and pull if you want but not if you are careful).<br>
<br>
(they removed aggro entirely)<br>
<br>
Now, was it my genius and excellence that made this all happen?  Hell no, they probably deleted everything I sent to them after laughing, but the point is... maybe not every person who mentions something they'd like to see changed or a problem is a whiner that you should stomp on and yell at.  In fact, Verant just might see the discussion and decide those aren't so bad ideas after all.  That's how we got:<br>
<br>
Ice Comet quest<br>
Rend<br>
Concussion<br>
Chill Sight<br>
Heat Sight<br>
all the post 50 spell lines Draught, Lure, and Banes<br>
Elnericks and Garrisons level 60 spells<br>
Garrisons Might Mana Shock at level 20<br>
<br>
